 target=\"_blank\">https://www.mims.com/malaysia/image/info/betaserc%20tab%2024%20mg/24%20mg</a><br />\n<br />\n無事啦</blockquote>上面開唔到<br />\n<a href=\"https://mediview.smugmug.com/keyword/289/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmediview.smugmug.com%2Fkeyword%2F289%2F&d=1TjRAgKfIFbsuTug5DMmHbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=46057527\" target=\"_blank\">https://mediview.smugmug.com/keyword/289/</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a603caf1b7abc66355b43ade1b76ce7d1ab238","tid":637673,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"樓主都on99 答畫胃藥就胃藥la 傻西"},{"pid":"acf6004cd73b48a61d7272baad8493e42fc08b30","tid":637673,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a30dc72c9323b67d8a2a0602c08e3490ac995f2","tid":637673,"uid":39316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:14:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知 見過都唔記得啦講真 一黎如果佢外國嘅佢d藥香港未必有<br />\n二黎個樣咁普通 點記得</blockquote><br />\nsorry係我無講清楚，唔好意思<br />\n係我住緊外國，女友係香港，佢之前黎探我住我度時跌左粒藥丸所以我先有得影低"},{"pid":"4f8ad6b110416ffa4e8e0caedfc6044875674669","tid":637673,"uid":1893,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:30:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.chien-yu.com.tw/dept/medicine_change_info_detail.php?id=13\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chien-yu.com.tw%2Fdept%2Fmedicine_change_info_detail.php%3Fid%3D13&d=1TjRAgKfIFbsuTug5DMmHbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=0231aa71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chien-yu.com.tw/dept/medicine_change_info_detail.php?id=13</a><br />\n<br />\n成分：Betahistine dihydrochloride                                          <br />\n中文名：寧耳眩<br />\n廠商：健康化學<br />\n機轉：1.改善內耳血行障礙：可弛緩內耳血管系之毛細管前括約肌，調整血管運動，增加內耳血流量約50%以上，可增加內頸動脈血流50%以上，與事前服用的抗組織胺劑無拮抗作用。 <br />\n      2.消散內淋巴水腫：提高毛細管壁的透過性，促進細胞外液的逆吸收，使內淋巴水腫消散。<br />\n適應症：梅尼爾氏症候群引起之眩暈、聽力障礙。<br />\n用法用量：成人1次1～2錠，1日3次，飯後服用。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">副作用：輕微胃炎</span>、皮疹及蕁麻疹。<br />\n<br />\n副作用係胃炎，點解會係胃藥嘅？"},{"pid":"9df5a0893842f4265be47ccf89888ce430d3e8dc","tid":637673,"uid":120772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f8db3cae3bf45cc1c4c3477c6c179d567ea5de8","tid":637673,"uid":39316,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>避孕藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好玩啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:33:50.000Z","msg":"避孕藥中間有條線俾你啪一半？咪玩喇 我真係未見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081c07274c0662036e40e0ae632c08945f73377f","tid":637673,"uid":1893,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:34:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.bh.cmu.edu.tw/cmubh/drug/drug_main_3.php?&amp;drug_id=431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bh.cmu.edu.tw%2Fcmubh%2Fdrug%2Fdrug_main_3.php%3F%26drug_id%3D431&d=1TjRAgKfIFbsuTug5DMmHbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=1314e25b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bh.cmu.edu.tw/cmubh/drug/drug_main_3.php?&amp;drug_id=431</a><br />\n<br />\n中文名稱：寧耳眩錠<br />\n英文名稱：Nilasen Tablet <br />\n成分及含量：Betahistine Dihydrochloride 16mg/Tab<br />\n藥品類別：口服藥  <br />\n作用：<span style=\"color: red;\">梅尼艾氏症候群</span>所引起之眩暈、聽力障礙<br />\n<br />\n基督教聯合醫院耳鼻喉科副顧問醫生關敏怡表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">耳水不平衡是「梅尼爾氏症」（M&eacute;ni&egrave;re's Disease）的俗稱</span>，由於「耳水不平衡」廣為人知曉，暈眩病人經常錯誤自我診斷患上梅尼爾氏症。香港未有梅尼爾氏症患者的相關統計紀錄，但有外國文獻指出，於頭暈診所的個案中，梅尼爾氏症的患者只佔5%。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/HealthNet/content.php?artid=1788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FHealthNet%2Fcontent.php%3Fartid%3D1788&d=1TjRAgKfIFbsuTug5DMmHbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=353d5ff4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/HealthNet/content.php?artid=1788</a><br />\n<br />\n你女友有耳水不平衡<br />\n真係冇事嘅"},{"pid":"f1fcdbd3cd530883661192fcf300ab026972959e","tid":637673,"uid":85416,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:46:50.000Z","msg":"你做人男友都幾撚得意<br />\n食藥都要俾你查下係乜"},{"pid":"1751e092f35502600943dec3aab395a772d497db","tid":637673,"uid":159869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ccea248dbba7ae47f099945328f08a53e984886","tid":637673,"uid":76488,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"d3ff7be23cdd66f057c3e0ab6ddcdc28070a8d58","tid":637673,"uid":39316,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T10:09:16.000Z","msg":"有無藥劑師或者執開藥既護士巴絲可以幫下手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T10:29:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">善存</span>"},{"pid":"0116e64a35a4de65201c398566b278ddef2d065c","tid":637673,"uid":39316,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你做人男友都幾撚得意<br />\n食藥都要俾你查下係乜</blockquote><br />\n就係見佢唔想講又求其答咁，擔心佢係咪有咩事唔話我知等我一個係外國唔洗咁掛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解耳水不平衡見暈都唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045070d31c9c8ff40b56968ed31a08dd0a683c3a","tid":637673,"uid":34910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"081c07274c0662036e40e0ae632c08945f73377f","tid":637673,"uid":1893,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:34:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.bh.cmu.edu.tw/cmubh/drug/drug_main_3.php?&amp;drug_id=431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bh.cmu.edu.tw%2Fcmubh%2Fdrug%2Fdrug_main_3.php%3F%26drug_id%3D431&d=1TjRAgKfIFbsuTug5DMmHbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=1314e25b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bh.cmu.edu.tw/cmubh/drug/drug_main_3.php?&amp;drug_id=431</a><br />\n<br />\n中文名稱：寧耳眩錠<br />\n英文名稱：Nilasen Tablet <br />\n成分及含量：Betahistine Dihydrochloride 16mg/Tab<br />\n藥品類別：口服藥  <br />\n作用：<span style=\"color: red;\">梅尼艾氏症候群</span>所引起之眩暈、聽力障礙<br />\n<br />\n基督教聯合醫院耳鼻喉科副顧問醫生關敏怡表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">耳水不平衡是「梅尼爾氏症」（M&eacute;ni&egrave;re's Disease）的俗稱</span>，由於「耳水不平衡」廣為人知曉，暈眩病人經常錯誤自我診斷患上梅尼爾氏症。香港未有梅尼爾氏症患者的相關統計紀錄，但有外國文獻指出，於頭暈診所的個案中，梅尼爾氏症的患者只佔5%。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/HealthNet/content.php?artid=1788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FHealthNet%2Fcontent.php%3Fartid%3D1788&d=1TjRAgKfIFbsuTug5DMmHbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=353d5ff4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/HealthNet/content.php?artid=1788</a><br />\n<br />\n你女友有耳水不平衡<br />\n真係冇事嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T15:37:35.000Z","msg":"可能醫生連埋胃藥開 攪錯咗姐<br />\n利申 9up"},{"pid":"0ddeb5c13fdcc0115f25e48d1712be0751f553ac","tid":637673,"uid":135278,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T15:48:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.chien-yu.com.tw/dept/medicine_change_info_detail.php?id=13\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chien-yu.com.tw%2Fdept%2Fmedicine_change_info_detail.php%3Fid%3D13&d=1TjRAgKfIFbsuTug5DMmHbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=0231aa71\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chien-yu.com.tw/dept/medicine_change_info_detail.php?id=13</a><br />\n<br />\n成分：Betahistine dihydrochloride                                          <br />\n中文名：寧耳眩<br />\n廠商：健康化學<br />\n機轉：1.改善內耳血行障礙：可弛緩內耳血管系之毛細管前括約肌，調整血管運動，增加內耳血流量約50%以上，可增加內頸動脈血流50%以上，與事前服用的抗組織胺劑無拮抗作用。 <br />\n      2.消散內淋巴水腫：提高毛細管壁的透過性，促進細胞外液的逆吸收，使內淋巴水腫消散。<br />\n適應症：梅尼爾氏症候群引起之眩暈、聽力障礙。<br />\n用法用量：成人1次1～2錠，1日3次，飯後服用。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">副作用：輕微胃炎</span>、皮疹及蕁麻疹。<br />\n<br />\n副作用係胃炎，點解會係胃藥嘅？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n膠完未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n張相完全唔一樣"},{"pid":"30e48217fc866dcb2569f81a2395a3701612e990","tid":637673,"uid":1893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ddeb5c13fdcc0115f25e48d1712be0751f553ac","tid":637673,"uid":135278,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T15:48:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.chien-yu.com.tw/dept/medicine_change_info_detail.php?id=13\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chien-yu.com.tw%2Fdept%2Fmedicine_change_info_detail.php%3Fid%3D13&d=1TjRAgKfIFbsuTug5DMmHbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=0231aa71\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chien-yu.com.tw/dept/medicine_change_info_detail.php?id=13</a><br />\n<br />\n成分：Betahistine dihydrochloride                                          <br />\n中文名：寧耳眩<br />\n廠商：健康化學<br />\n機轉：1.改善內耳血行障礙：可弛緩內耳血管系之毛細管前括約肌，調整血管運動，增加內耳血流量約50%以上，可增加內頸動脈血流50%以上，與事前服用的抗組織胺劑無拮抗作用。 <br />\n      2.消散內淋巴水腫：提高毛細管壁的透過性，促進細胞外液的逆吸收，使內淋巴水腫消散。<br />\n適應症：梅尼爾氏症候群引起之眩暈、聽力障礙。<br />\n用法用量：成人1次1～2錠，1日3次，飯後服用。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">副作用：輕微胃炎</span>、皮疹及蕁麻疹。<br />\n<br />\n副作用係胃炎，點解會係胃藥嘅？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n膠完未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n張相完全唔一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T15:52:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mediview.smugmug.com/keyword/289/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F